('10000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001', '10000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001', 'What is Vibe Coding?', 'Welcome to the future of software development. In this lesson, you will discover Vibe Coding—a revolutionary approach where humans focus on intent, systems, and outcomes while AI handles the execution. This is not about learning to write code the old way. This is about learning to build software the way it''s actually done in 2025.

