('10000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000009', '10000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005', 'Devin, OpenHands, and Claude Computer Use', 'Welcome to the frontier of Vibe Coding: Agentic Tools. These are AI systems that don''t just respond to prompts—they autonomously plan, execute, and iterate on complex development tasks. This lesson introduces you to Devin, OpenHands, and Claude Computer Use.

