('10000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000011', '10000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006', 'From Prototype to Production with Vercel and Supabase', 'Building software is only valuable if people can use it. This lesson teaches you how to deploy your Vibe-coded projects to production using Vercel for hosting and Supabase for backend services.

